Package org.usfirst.frc.team5585.robot.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArcadeDrive
    default drive command.
    autoDrive
    drives the robot forward for a set time.
    baselineAuto
    command group to score over the baseline.
    CenterAuto
    command group to score on the center gear peg.
    changeCameraDirection
    Changes the camera direction widget on the smartdashboard.
    DisableDrive
    disables the robot drive.
    PreciseDrive
    runs the precise drive method in the drivetrain subsystem.
    RunLift
    calls the op control method of the lift subsystem.
    score_forward
    subsidiary auto command.
    score_reverse
    drives backward away from the gear peg.
    switchCameraToFront
    switches the camera to the front camera (as defined by server 17)
    switchCameraToRear
    switches the camera to the rear camera (as defined by server 17)
